SECONDS:
select J.bvs_job_id, T.SECONDS, O.job_option_id,
J.request_entered_timestamp, J.requester_uuid, J.start_date, J.end_date, 
TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR, J.start_date, J.end_date) as
QUERY_RANGE_HOURS,
J.caid, J.requester_firm_id, J.requester_account_id, J.hits
from bvs_client_jobs J, bvs_client_jobs_options 
O,
(

select bvs_job_id, TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, min(timestamp), max(timestamp)) as 
SECONDS
from bvsm_job_state_history
where new_state in ('processing', 'secomplete') and
bvs_job_id in
(
select bvs_job_id from
(
select HH.bvs_job_id as bvs_job_id, HH.new_state as new_state, count(*) as 
Total from
bvsm_job_state_history HH, bvs_client_jobs_options OO
WHERE HH.bvs_job_id = OO.bvs_job_id
and HH.new_state in ('processing', 'secomplete')
and OO.job_option_id IN (4,7,33,34,5,6,7,8,12,18,23,28,36,43,48,51)
group by HH.bvs_job_id, HH.new_state having count(*) = 1
) JobIDWithUniqueStates
group by bvs_job_id having count(*) = 2
)
group by bvs_job_id

) T

WHERE J.bvs_job_id = O.bvs_job_id and
O.job_option_id IN (4,7,33,34,5,6,7,8,12,18,23,28,36,43,48,51) and T.bvs_job_id 
= J.bvs_job_id
